A. Router only
B. Monitored hosts
C. Firewall only
D. IDS manager

9. A simulated attack is useful to:
A. Damage system
B. Test IDS effectiveness
C. Replace firewall
D. Improve bandwidth

10. Monitoring RAM and disk usage helps to detect:
A. Encryption
B. Resource exhaustion
C. Phishing
D. Spoofing

